datasets.name: dataset_18
queryLines: SELECT Home_Tile AS Home_Tile, MEASURE(f_ctr_cta1) AS Percent_Primary_Button_Clicked_vs_Interstitial_Displayed, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Tile_Views) AS Total_Unique_Tile_Views, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Tile_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Tile_Clicks, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Interstitial_Views) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Views, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Interstitial_Primary_Button_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Primary_Button_Clicks, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Interstitial_Secondary_Button_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Secondary_Button_Clicks FROM hpx_events_model_homepage_summary GROUP BY Home_Tile ORDER BY f_ctr_cta1 DESC

value.displayName: % Primary Button Clicked Vs Interstitial Displayed
